description: This file serves as the entry point for a React-based web application. It imports core React libraries, styles, and the main App component, then renders the App component into the DOM element with id 'root' within a React.StrictMode wrapper.

methods.name: ReactDOM.createRoot
methods.description: Creates a root React DOM node for rendering the React component tree.

methods.name: root.render
methods.description: Renders the specified React elements into the root DOM node.
